__ Cantrip: Fleas ____________________________ Cost: 5 _______________________

Use:  cantrip fleas < target >                 Material Component: creature
Use:  C fleas < target >                       

The cantrip fleas is a minor magic of the sphere of conjuration.  When the
cantrip is traced, the caster summons a horde of fleas and directs them
towards a creature.  While fleas do no real damage to a creature, they are
guaranteed to be quite annoying.
